_DATA	SEGMENT
??_C@_0CDH@BPJH@Master?0?5I?5have?5a?5strange?5experie@ DB 'Master, I hav'
	DB	'e a strange experience to relate. I know that you have a grea'
	DB	't knowledge of those monstrosities that inhabit the labyrinth'
	DB	', and this is something that I cannot understand for the very'
	DB	' life of me... I was awakened during the night by a scraping '
	DB	'sound just outside of my tavern. When I looked out from my be'
	DB	'droom, I saw the shapes of small demon-like creatures in the '
	DB	'inn yard. After a short time, they ran off, but not before st'
	DB	'ealing the sign to my inn. I don''t know why the demons would'
	DB	' steal my sign but leave my family in peace... ''tis strange,'
	DB	' no? |', 00H				; `string'
_DATA	ENDS
